data.description: This delightful three-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch-style home exudes charm and warmth. The generously sized living room is bathed in natural sunlight, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and socializing. The kitchen, featuring updated cabinets and modern appliances, offers ample space for gatherings and culinary adventures. Embrace the practicality of low-maintenance tile and wood laminate floors, providing aesthetic appeal and ease of care. Step outside to discover a covered carport and a delightful patio for entertaining, providing a perfect setting for al fresco dining and gatherings. The large fenced yard offers a private oasis. This home is conveniently located, with shopping amenities just a stone's throw away and downtown mere minutes from your doorstep. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and accessibility in this wonderful abode.
